      "name": "套裝",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "artifact_list",
          "data": {
            "circlet_of_logos": {
              "desc": "<p>鑲嵌著紫水晶與祖母綠的冠冕，似乎是古代花神祭司的頭飾。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/13/7998136/d0dac0543a776782f0496bf908870291_2903807487638210412.png",
              "id": "artifact50453",
              "key": "circlet_of_logos",
              "posKey": "circlet_of_logos",
              "posName": "理之冠",
              "position": "理之冠",
              "title": "紫晶的花冠"
            },
            "flower_of_life": {
              "desc": "<p>精雕細琢的紫水晶之花，其形態描摹了一種近乎絕跡的古代花朵。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/13/7998136/50ce09dfa5a91a33aa9cedfb15bcf2d1_6221184897874592291.png",
              "id": "artifact79067",
              "key": "flower_of_life",
              "posKey": "flower_of_life",
              "posName": "生之花",
              "position": "生之花",
              "title": "月女的華彩"
            },
            "goblet_of_eonothem": {
              "desc": "<p>紫色水晶雕成的小瓶，以祖母綠的瓶蓋緊緊封裝著。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/13/7998136/f4e5dde048f278e01371e56637a7bd1f_1934296325657108154.png",
              "id": "artifact13748",
              "key": "goblet_of_eonothem",
              "posKey": "goblet_of_eonothem",
              "posName": "空之杯",
              "position": "空之杯",
              "title": "守秘的魔瓶"
            },
            "plume_of_death": {
              "desc": "<p>早已絕跡的鳥類留下的羽毛，被古代花神的信徒鑲嵌了亮麗的黃金與寶石。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/13/7998136/30b5885215b1c09b6033b5cafe437d2c_3180837893001645145.png",
              "id": "artifact75350",
              "key": "plume_of_death",
              "posKey": "plume_of_death",
              "posName": "死之羽",
              "position": "死之羽",
              "title": "謝落的筵席"
            },
            "sands_of_eon": {
              "desc": "<p>不再流動的沙漏，無論如何顛倒，都不再回應時間的流動。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/13/7998136/baf7c8bd6eba7afe0c71c9bf8cc6f96b_6354422909012506449.png",
              "id": "artifact50638",
